    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/c5d0fb0aacb415aa384af9436c14db0f.poster.avif?t=1771859965\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/c5d0fb0aacb415aa384af9436c14db0f.webm?t=1771859965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/c5d0fb0aacb415aa384af9436c14db0f.mp4?t=1771859965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of Karakuri Ninja VR with this exciting demo! Learn to wield powerful weapons and master ninjutsu as you face off against formidable enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo includes a tutorial stage and one route with four action-packed stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/dd92cbf48a835996e71cb9c7c016ebad.poster.avif?t=1771859965\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/dd92cbf48a835996e71cb9c7c016ebad.webm?t=1771859965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/dd92cbf48a835996e71cb9c7c016ebad.mp4?t=1771859965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage features a variety of weapons such as Japanese swords, kunai, and shuriken, as well as items that enhance weapons to advance the battle situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players who are skilled ninja can use special ninjutsu such as energy balls and aura shields.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/73f621c8a45a3b1d5bd21861a298a0af.poster.avif?t=1771859965\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/73f621c8a45a3b1d5bd21861a298a0af.webm?t=1771859965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/73f621c8a45a3b1d5bd21861a298a0af.mp4?t=1771859965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, enemies also attack with fire and lightning ninjutsu. In a ninja fight, one must carefully observe the enemy's actions and never miss the moment to strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Karakuri Ninja VR, as you progress through the stages, more powerful enemies will appear. Hone your swordsmanship and ninjutsu skills and face them bravely.</p>",
